data.description: A stunningly updated & meticulously cared for 2-story, nestled in a wonderful neighborhood & prime Urbandale location with easy access to I-80/35! Lovely curb appeal welcomes you home to an open floor plan. All neutral colors throughout. Combined sitting/dining room has lots of natural light. Cooking is a delight in the updated kitchen featuring abundant white cabinetry, granite counters, GE Profile appliances & eat-in dining. Slider access to a spacious 2 tier deck with built-in seating & limestone patio. Great room features a large window with freshly painted white floor-to-ceiling built-ins & gas fireplace. Wired for TV above fireplace. Laundry room includes washer/dryer/frig. Half bath completes main level. Upstairs flex space is perfect for playroom or office. 4 bedrooms upstairs with 2nd full bath & dual sinks. Master bedroom offers spacious en-suite with dual vanity, jetted tub, shower & walk-in closet. Finished LL has a sizable space with 2nd gas fireplace, built-ins, 3/4 bathroom & ample storage including space for 5th bedroom with closet. Wired for built-in surround sound & wall-mounted TV. Outside offers prof landscaping & mature trees with irrigation & Invisible Fence. 3-car garage has stylish carriage doors. Only a few steps to Deer Ridge Park & Raccoon River Valley Trail with biking & walking paths. Upgrades too numerous to list include custom closet inserts upstairs.
